{"tid":1645054,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【盲點】警方今次為咗避嫌而延遲確認死者身份  下次藍絲殺人都可以Close file","createTime":"2019-10-10T18:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T04:13:07.000Z","uid":15696,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6261a21503f2d737b5ef8acc1c3aa528c1a76a85","tid":1645054,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:13:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果藍絲 / 強姦犯 真係殺咗你<br />\n<br />\n警方為咗避嫌而低調處理<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界會點 ?<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n無論真相係點，<span style=\"color: red;\">警方故意低調處理案件係事實</span>，<br />\n比照失蹤人口，其實好快已經可以確認死者身份，例如高秀蘭自殺案件。<br />\n而女死者9月19日已經係失蹤人口，警方其實<span style=\"color: red;\">一早已經知道死者身份</span>。<br />\n甚至VTC上星期已經得知陳彥霖死訊，並可以回應媒體。<br />\n蘋果亦多次查詢但係10月5日先回應事主<span style=\"color: red;\">為15歲失蹤女童，仍唔肯確認浮屍身份</span>。<br />\n直至蘋果要<span style=\"color: red;\">口頭質詢，警方先於10月9日口頭確認</span>，油塘浮屍身份是失蹤陳姓女童。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191011/60139820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191011%2F60139820&d=tgdX0zC4r3YoKKw%2Bq%2FbDqSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=76412a72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191011%2F60139820&h=aabbc9d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191011/60139820</a><br />\n<br />\n如果因為死者身份敏感而要低調查案，唁肯確認浮屍身份，<br />\n延遲公佈 = 少咗線索<br />\n警方嘅所謂專業(我唔覺得有)去咗邊? <br />\n係咪做任何事受政治審查 ?<br />\n<br />\n今次可以因為你黃色唔確認身份<br />\n下次就可以因為你黃色 有可疑都唔查案<br />\n警方做法一直以嚟都係鼓勵緊人去傷害示威者<br />\n由報警唔捉人 到因為避嫌而低調處理<br />\n藍絲真係會覺得殺人冇後果"},{"pid":"eb75d8ca58100d954a7571912e0bdebbbc92cf18","tid":1645054,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:15:08.000Z","msg":"Pk"},{"pid":"fc3ece8602fc03a769cb345055e47cf66d97c20e","tid":1645054,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:15:19.000Z","msg":"傳媒曾多次去信查詢，警方疑因死者身份敏感，耗時多日才確認浮屍身份。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06b29ac19cc7115ff3033a57d56313045b132d6","tid":1645054,"uid":68366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:15:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b63f747a2f90d5ade2249304b19e52d53e22604","tid":1645054,"uid":68366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:16:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dbf6428a9f3e4b48bb721eb6a0d9c134205edf3","tid":1645054,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:17:41.000Z","msg":"真私了先係王道"},{"pid":"f4f20efe321d544be6f8400a42ee8bb1dab48735","tid":1645054,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:19:07.000Z","msg":"我知大家好關注查案<br />\n但大家都冇針對返呢點 其實係好醜惡恐怖<br />\n只要你係黃色 /示威者 死咗可以連公平 都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751bcb91eba716a8613bff68f8272bdffabc6d6e","tid":1645054,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb4347de040539d8a38e01be269e8c8ed4473cd9","tid":1645054,"uid":68366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:20:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"140ce7582ea7fe2214a5bdfe58f2b22f2961f649","tid":1645054,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:21:07.000Z","msg":"黑警：又有示威者死 反正唔關我事 為咗避嫌唔查啦　"},{"pid":"f7e88b0c4832bdfa69016cf08bf9e0940213f32c","tid":1645054,"uid":68366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:21:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pi